review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2021
name: Frank O.
title: Delicious but way too expensive
review: I absolutely LOVE this yogurt!I cannot describe the taste but it is so good, I love the texture of it too!The other thing I love about this yogurt is that it has the LOWEST fat content compared to other plant based yogurts. The problem is that it's hardly affordable, especially if you have an entire family that loves them too ... It's over $50 just for a week of yogurt and heaven forbid you eat two containers a night. For the average family, it's just not practical to purchase regularly but we do still purchase it as a special treat.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2021
name: LC
title: Outstanding vanilla flavor
review: You can actually see, taste, and smell REAL vanilla in this little cup and not the artificial kind! The yogurt itself tastes luxurious compared to other vanilla yogurt I’ve tried. It is pretty light, neutral and non acidic in taste. It does have added sugar but it’s not too sweet like some other yogurts with added sugar. It will go well with so many toppings. It’s pricey, but worth a try if you’re curious. I would stock up on some if it goes on sale.
